20 TECHNOLOGY OR A MEDICAL SAFETY DEVICE THAT IS:
21 1. A WEARABLE, PORTABLE, OR INTEGRATED
22 ELECTRONIC DEVICE OR SYSTEM THAT USES GLOBAL POSITIONING SYSTEM
23 TECHNOLOGY, RADIO FREQUENCY IDENTIFICATION TECHNOLOGY, BLUETOOTH, OR
24 SIMILAR TECHNOLOGY TO SUPPORT THE IDENTIFICATION, MONITORING, OR RAPID
